&lt;p data-start=&quot;317&quot; data-end=&quot;679&quot;&gt;Varda is looking for a hands-on &lt;strong&gt;Automation &amp;amp; Test&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;347&quot; data-end=&quot;380&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Intern&lt;/strong&gt; to support the design, build, and test of terrestrial hardware systems used in spacecraft and propulsion testing. This role offers a 50/50 split between lab work and desk engineering, ideal for candidates eager to apply their electrical and programming skills in a real-world aerospace environment.&lt;/p&gt;
